The input array `arr` is not null.
The input array `pieces` is not null.
The length of `pieces` is greater than or equal to 1.
The length of `arr` is greater than or equal to the length of `pieces`.
The sum of the lengths of all arrays in `pieces` is equal to the length of `arr`.
The integers in `arr` are distinct.
The integers in `pieces` are distinct.
